       \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/garmin-instinct-2-watch-face-tree.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/garmin-instinct-2-watch-face-tree.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/garmin-instinct-2-watch-face-tree.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/garmin-instinct-2-watch-face-tree.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2160\" height=\"1215\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The Garmin Instinct 2 Solar hanging from a tree.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/garmin-instinct-2-watch-face-tree.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/garmin-instinct-2-watch-face-tree.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-garmin-instinct-2-solar\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Garmin Instinct 2 Solar?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eFor the most part, you\u0026#39;re going to get a pretty solid smartwatch with the Instinct 2 Solar. But the real highlight of this watch is that it delivers up to 28 days of battery life on a single charge. Furthermore, if you manage to get it charged via solar each day, it can last forever without having to be plugged in. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThis is a huge perk, especially if you\u0026#39;re someone that\u0026#39;s always on the go, and maybe can\u0026#39;t plug in to charge the watch. When it comes to the design, this watch isn\u0026#39;t all that elegant, but it does pack a rugged design with a fiber-reinforced polymer case that\u0026#39;s meant to take on whatever you can throw at it. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIt has a monochrome transflective memory-in-pixel display that looks good in most conditions, and it also features a variety of sensors that can track your health and fitness metrics. You can also get a better picture thanks to the watch\u0026#39;s ability to track your sleep quality and stress levels. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eYou can even accurately track your hikes and jogs using multi-band GNSS, and get more detailed information about your whereabouts thanks to the built-in compass and barometric altimeter. While the watch comes pretty packed with features, you will have the ability to expand using the Garmin Connect IQ Store. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAnd since this is a smartwatch, you\u0026#39;ll get notifications on your wrist when connected to a smartphone. Just in case you ever leave your wallet at home, you can use Garmin Pay at compatible terminals to make purchases. For the most part, this is just a superb watch that gets a lot of things right. And you can\u0026#39;t really complain thanks to its recent price drop. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
